### Register a new user
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/accounts/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "mypassword123"
}


### Login with the user
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/accounts/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "mypassword123"
}

### Get user profile (replace {{token}} after login)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/accounts/profile/
Authorization: Token 123abc456def789ghi

### Update user profile
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/accounts/profile/
Content-Type: application/json
